                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-12-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 16, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Conger reports that the Russians are arranging with the Chinese Government
                    customs service for Talienwan and some interior Manchurian ports, similar to,
                    but independent of, the maritime customs, and under Russian commissioner instead
                    of English; post-offices under the same control.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
